{
  "stem": "13673.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But clothing, and she actually packed up what amounts to a trousseau, I think, you know, bed sheets and that sort of thing, which, to this day, I know I don't have them anymore, but I did have for a long time.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then this committee, the Refugee Committee, it was called, sent us the name of the family that I was to be with.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that family sent us some letters and a picture of themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I didn't actually go till March, so from November to March.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was still going to the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I learned about Purim and Haman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said Haman-- I told my mother that Haman's just like Hitler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she went pale because you're not allowed to say things, not even in your own house, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The saying used to be   that the walls had ears, and they might well have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just went on going to school because they weren't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jewish schoolmates, I don't even remember them anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I must have blocked a lot of stuff, and also it was such a short time from November to March that I--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my parents and I went in the business car to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody else drove us because neither of my parents drove.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Your father was still in business at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The business had been taken from him a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Since 1936 he had been forced to sell the business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is now 1930-- early 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was really in a-- but we still had a car available.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
